videos.description: Temple quarterback Anthony Russo drops a dime to Sean Ryan in stride for a 24-yard touchdown, putting Temple on the board first.
videos.headline: Temple QB threads the needle for 24-yard TD

videos.description: Anthony Russo throws up a 50-50 ball to wide receiver Branden Mack, who snatches the seven-yard pass for a Temple touchdown.
videos.headline: Temple QB connects for 2nd TD pass of 1st quarter

videos.description: Temple's Isaiah Wright turns on the burners and snaps tacklers' ankles en route to a 59-yard punt return touchdown.
videos.headline: Temple returner turns on jets for 59-yard TD

videos.description: Temple quarterback Anthony Russo continues his stellar first half with his third touchdown pass, this time to Isaiah Wright for a 19-yard score.
videos.headline: Temple's Russo delivers 3rd TD pass of half

videos.description: Temple quarterback Anthony Russo is on the money with a 31-yard touchdown whip to Randle Jones, who fends off his man and snags a nasty one-handed catch for the unreal score.
videos.headline: Temple WR only needs one hand for sick 31-yard TD

videos.description: Temple calls the number of Freddie Booth-Lloyd, its massive 330-pound defensive tackle for a 1-yard score as he lost his shoe in the pile.
videos.headline: Temple's 330-pound DT plows in for TD
